						div(class='jumbotron page-title')
							h1(style='font-size: 96pt;') Easy CTF
							h4 Another CTF competition for high schoolers, by high schoolers.
							h5
								a(href='http://goo.gl/jmpByq', target='_blank') November 29 to December 6
